It's all in the Bentley Manual, complete with pics--in glorious black & white.
This really is THE "must have" book.  Bus Depot has the best price I know of.

http://www.busdepot.com/ASP/more_books.asp?VehCod=B&PartType=M
see: "Official Volkswagen Repair Manual"

Harbor Freight has an inexpensive angle finder:
http://www.harborfreight.com/cpi/ctaf/Displayitem.taf?itemnumber=34214

There's also quite a bit of advice to be found in the List archives.

